sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35807ebb7f247973b901e6915ec3419ea2fe50c0","tid":361524,"uid":25955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"其實我都會坐係度柯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為企係度柯會有水花彈出黎  坐係度就柯完唔洗抹返 最煩係要禁低個龍頭 咁先唔會掂到廁板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2ace8695bd3329066597ec4d72d625191a5c10","tid":361524,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"撐你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申負皮"},{"pid":"216f9370979f4f2680a5360c6a4b23fb2af851e0","tid":361524,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係要負責洗廁所既話你就知彈左出嚟既尿花可以有幾臭。<br />\n你100%射中廁盆都有好多你眼睇唔到既尿花彈到周圍都係。<br />\n廁盆後面下面好難抹。<br />\n<br />\n利申，有尿兜既廁所或公廁先會企住痾。</blockquote><br />\n坐喺度啲尿咪又係彈落屎忽度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc5e4e372fedd4e33f7b190ee391037c224104a","tid":361524,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"企係度痾無問題，去完清潔返就ok"},{"pid":"b3abdf0cf98fa7e69b5546e07e878e14df0030c6","tid":361524,"uid":53194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個fd話佢全家男人都坐住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男性結構就係要企係道痾先合理，我覺得係天性黎，作為男人就要企係道痾。<br />\n<br />\n而且呢個方法仲節省時間，女人每次去都要成分鐘，男人企係度痾20-30秒搞掂。"},{"pid":"cfb555cc3207891f30b223f3b5fc6baa526c9dfd","tid":361524,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T08:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>企係度痾無問題，去完清潔返就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔俾，唔理你清唔清潔返，都要坐呢？（唔講可唔可以唔理佢照企果樣）"},{"pid":"bd92d3630cf4380e5b6155fdffc1b14b64bcfe80","tid":361524,"uid":2701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"s